<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一次又一次地把木桶放下去，赛伊觉得有些烦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人也想要放弃了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊深深地吐了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就这样吧。井里没什么特别的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一边说一边将最后一桶东西倒出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等。”潘瑟叫道，“看这个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她捡起了一块外形奇特的贝壳儿，上面有很多泥浆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她凑近了去看那个东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟抹去了一些泥浆，把它拿在手里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它很美。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得这是个贝壳。”她回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她开始抹去余下的泥浆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，那个贝壳开始咯咯笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟吓了一大跳，差点儿扔了它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它笑了！”鲍比大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“里面有东西。”他在壳状物上敲了敲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢！别这样！”壳状物叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都你看看我我看看你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，最奇妙的事情发生了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个生物从壳子里探出头来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它有着海马的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它的脖子和背上有不断开合的闪闪发光的鳍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当它的脑袋左右转动时，那对儿鳍也闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们第一次遇到这种奇事，都愣住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了？”那个生物生气地问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，潘瑟开口了：“你是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个生物盯着他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我就告诉你们。”它开始说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们朝我扔东西，把我吵醒了。”它盯着简。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是你一开始拿走我的东西。”它看着赛伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你挠我痒痒。”它瞪着潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，你在我的壳上敲来敲去！”鲍比低头看着地面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你们告诉我说你们连我是谁都不知道？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们尴尬地盯着地面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真对不起！”简抱歉地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不知道你在井里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个生物什么都没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会，它的鳍不再闪光了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我接受你们的道歉。”最后它说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们真的不知道你是谁。”赛伊迅速补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是奥伦八世，”它郑重地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是我们种族在整个海洋里的第八代。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇。”孩子们齐声叫出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过你们可以叫我休伊。”那个生物笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们的脸上还是一片茫然，显然他们还是不知道他到底是谁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们知道什么是奥伦吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“实际上不知道。”简替所有人回答了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊猛地闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脑袋快速地左右转动着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从前，”他说，“我们奥伦是海洋里最有名的神秘生物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是说，你是个妖精？”鲍比打断了他的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妖精？噢，我的天，哦，我的天哪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊的鳍又开始一边发光一边不断快速地扇动着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请不要生气，休伊。”简说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比的意思并不是要把你叫成妖精。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那好吧。”休伊平静地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奥伦拥有天赐的能力，可以让其他人实现任何愿望。”他继续说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是说，你可以让愿望成真？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊点点头，然后其他孩子就和鲍比一起开心地大叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，”休伊提高声音道，“你们必须保证两件事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要能实现愿望，我们任何事情都愿意做！”简拍手道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊继续说下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，”他说，“你们一天只可以许一个愿望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二，在许下愿望之后，你们必须将我送回井里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>365212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这听起来并不是很难。”赛伊笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>365213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>368313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，”休伊笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>368314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>373341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“日落的时候，一切都会恢复到原来的样子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>373342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>382766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是说，我们的愿望只能实现一天？”鲍比用失望的语气问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>382767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>390731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”休伊回答之后就消失在了他的壳里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>